texts.text: This pig's heart is not was I was hoping for, but it will do.
This shall become the core of my new sun.
You monster. Return that heart to us at once.
There's no point.
He's dead...
Yes, he is indeed dead.
But in the hands of a god of creation, such as Tezcatlipoca and I,
it is possible to revive him if his heart is returned to him.
Say what?!
Once you return his heart to him, it can be massaged while I breathe life back into him.
Then this one will be able to return to life.
What? Why would I help you do that?
I vowed to never work with you ever again.
Give it back.
Let's take it back.
Oh? You seem awful confident in yourself.
If you want it back so much, come and get it!
Yo, you got it!

Let's do this, y'all!
Devil Download!
Go!
There!
Attacking me all at once? Not bad.
Let me give you a taste of what I can do.
>Jaguars appear out of nowhere in front of Tezcatlipoca.
*Growl*
Jaguars...?!
Yo, how many of them are there...?!

*Laugh*
All clones of myself! Now, attack!
>The jaguars charge while brandishing their sharp claws.
There's too many! We gotta play some defense for now!

Got it!
Devil Download!
>Demons surround the Liberators and protect them from the jaguars.
*Growl*
>Your formation is about to break...!
I will take care of them!
*Wince*
*Growl*
*Groan*
No, it's too much for even Quetzalcoatl...!
They're about to break through...!
Just hold out... A little longer...!

*Laugh*
Out of moves?
We have to attack Tezcatlipoca himself...
Wait, Shiori, what do you plan on doing?!
Shionyan, no! It's too dangerous!
We won't get anywhere at this rate.
Come back.
Please.
Don't worry.
>Shiori walks out and into the prowl of jaguars.
*Growl*
Devil... Download...
>The jaguars begin clawing away at Shiori's skin.

No, Shiori...
She isn't stopping...!
*Growl*
*Wince*
Dammit, we're too busy defendin' ourselves here...!
Ain't no way we can get to Shionyan's position now!

Ah, Shionyan...!
I sense your spirit!
You are indeed a worthy sacrifice!
You, Shionyan, is it? I shall protect you.
You're the one that can bring Meat back to life, right?
If you die here, we won't be able to save him even if we do get his heart back.
On top of that, a good chunk of you is scattered to pieces.
If you're not at full strength, please, go back and help my friends.
Such a strong girl...
Allow me to at least aid you in this manner.
>Quetzalcoatl's wings begin to shine and cast a light on Shiori.
I feel... Stronger...
Like you just injected me with something...
Thanks. I think I can fight my way to Tezcatlipoca now.

*Wince*
Devil Download!
>Shiori makes it past the jaguars and to Tezcatlipoca.
*Pant*
>Shiori is bleeding profusely from her claw lacerations.
You made it past my jaguars. Well done, my dear!
Since you have come this far, I believe it is my turn now.
>Tezcatlipoca morphs into a jaguar.
Let us see which is faster. A human or a jaguar.
Now, face me!
>Tezcatlipoca leaps forward to closes in on Shiori.
>He points his claws directly at Shiori...
Breathe...
>They parry.
What...?!
>Tezcatlipoca collapses.
>Blood begins trickling from Shiori's cheek.
Heh...
>Shiori looks down upon Tezcatlipoca.
I should not have made... So many... Clones...
>Tezcatlipoca returns to his original form.
>Gakuto's heart falls out of his hand.
>Shiori picks it up without a second thought.
He might be a fat pig, but I'd rather not be without him.
>Nobody is around to hear Shiori utter those words.
